<item>
            <title>[CXF-4469] 2.6.x rt-ws-security bundle is requiring opensaml</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-4469</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The CXF&apos;s 2.6.x&apos;s rt-ws-security bundle is requiring opensaml, although opensaml is supposed to be optional.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The cxf all bundle declares opensaml* as optional and not requiring them.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The rt-ws-security&apos;s pom also needs this optional import declaration.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
